Text: Just wondering if this is the "Clean" version which used to be added on here, as i haven't seen them in a long while. Think it was made by Clean2k5?
Nope I just build a new cvs clean version about once a week and decided to just start posting them for anyone else who likes the latest builds, without all the extra scripts and stuff.
Thanks, thats really great. All the extra scripts was killing my box slowly:-) Nice to have a new clean version again.
